# Error Documentation Template

Use this template when documenting a new error. Copy this file and rename to `{error-type}.mdc`.

## Error: [Error Name]

**Summary**: One-sentence description of the error

**Root Cause**: Why this error occurs (the underlying reason)

**Symptoms**: 
- How the error manifests
- Error messages seen
- Unexpected behavior observed

**Prevention**: 
- How to avoid this error in the future
- Code patterns that prevent it

**Fix**: 
- Step-by-step resolution
- Code changes needed

**Example**:
```python
# Before (causes error)
problematic_code()

# After (fixed)
corrected_code()
```

